  - Filler
  - Image importer
    - image gallery, sticky notes
  - Lazo selection tool
  - Move
  - Copy/paste
  - Multi pointer support 
  - Define a configuration file and settings
    - select workspace
    - preferred colors
    - thickness size 
  - Zoom and rotate 

